text: David Leitch (born February 7, 1970) is an American actor who co-directed John Wick (2014) and was also the director of Atomic Blonde (2017), Deadpool 2 (2018), and Hobbs & Shaw (2019). He was born in Kohler, Wisconsin. == Other websites == * Category:1975 births Category:Living people Category:American movie actors Category:Movie directors from Wisconsin Category:Movie producers from Wisconsin Category:Actors from Wisconsin
